{"type": "article", "id": 22750, "title": "2升果汁瓶包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-24T07:30:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 75, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021646581Oof0p4qCaXlubS7.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一个可容纳 2 升果汁的包装，它的外形近似花蕊。瓶身像是三个波浪连起来的，削弱了大容量的笨重感，反而增加了光泽度。其中一个凸出来的结构镂空，成为手柄，可以增加倾倒的稳定性。多个水瓶可以沿着三角形结构的凹凸侧面放置，也比圆形水瓶更稳定。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164655LjimyXKDeS4MQuxC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164656om2tijsL0qB7wUhp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164656QIW73lPJHZvczMkC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164657SAiqhEl5D8uFrZIM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164657KxCN164FsGEhaMlm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}